---
title: Mario Batali's Spaghetti with Fresh Tomatoes, Chorizo, and Basil
description: Even the best recipes get even better when you're cooking for a good goal. Mario Batali's vibrant spaghetti dish was specially crafted for EAT (RED) SAVE LIVES. Featuring juicy, warm heirloom tomatoes, browned and crisped chorizo, and pasta cooked to a perfect al dente, it’s hearty, satisfying, and can be adjusted to match your ideal level of heat. As Mario says, Ain’t it delicious when good food does great things?
